    <svcsection id="EGES265-Section2" svcsectype="enginesec" division="engine" date="03/25/04">
        <title>EVRT&#174; Electronically Controlled Turbocharger</title>
        <description>
            <geninfo>
                <para>See for complete description of the EVRT&#174; electronically controlled turbocharger.</para>
                <para>This engine is equipped with a EVRT&#174; electronically controlled turbocharger. For the
                    procedures in this manual, the term Variable Geometry Turbocharger (VGT) will be used.
                </para>
                <para>Major VGT assembly components are not serviceable individually. When turbocharger issues arise,
                    remove the VGT and perform an initial inspection.
                </para>
            </geninfo>
        </description>
